 And let us see and feel your goodness.

1042
00:43:13,400 --> 00:43:16,440
 In the presence of our enemies,

1043
00:43:16,440 --> 00:43:17,840
 remind us that you are here.

1044
00:43:17,840 --> 00:43:22,040
 In the midst of the challenges that we face,

1045
00:43:22,040 --> 00:43:26,040
 give us a peace that allows us to drop our weapons,

1046
00:43:26,040 --> 00:43:28,800
 to be still and know that you are God.

1047
00:43:31,760 --> 00:43:32,760
 And fill us up, Lord,

1048
00:43:32,760 --> 00:43:34,680
 to the point that our cups overflow.

1049
00:43:34,680 --> 00:43:40,040
 And may your goodness and mercy follow us

1050
00:43:40,040 --> 00:43:42,120
 all the days of our lives.

1051
00:43:42,120 --> 00:43:43,080
 And we thank you.

1052
00:43:43,080 --> 00:43:51,120
 That we will never walk alone,

1053
00:43:51,120 --> 00:43:52,360
 because you never let go.

1054
00:43:52,360 --> 00:43:55,280
 Amen.

1055
